galedric.events.schedulers

Interface EventScheduler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PriorityEventScheduler, QueueEventScheduler

    public interface EventScheduler
    The event scheduler interface. An event scheduler must keep a list of events to deliver and decide of an order in their delivery.
